you got there.

33:01.938 --> 33:04.857
Yeah, yeah, he
is adorable, isn't he?

33:04.941 --> 33:06.734
Got a daughter myself.

33:06.860 --> 33:09.820
Huh. I'll take $20
on two, please.

33:09.946 --> 33:12.490
No gas. Pump's broke.
Been broke for months.

33:12.616 --> 33:15.076
Oh, shit, all right.

33:15.202 --> 33:19.914
Would you grab me a can of that
Black Bear Longcut Wintergreen?

33:24.378 --> 33:26.962
You don't want any
trouble now, do you?

33:29.633 --> 33:31.050
- Open it up.
- Yeah.

33:31.176 --> 33:33.135
Ain't much in there.

33:33.261 --> 33:34.970
Well, that'll do.

33:37.974 --> 33:39.892
Boy, what are you doing?
Come on!

33:39.976 --> 33:41.102
This ain't no fucking library!
Hurry up!

33:41.228 --> 33:43.270
Quit pissing around!

33:43.397 --> 33:44.480
Now get back there
and clean that up.

33:44.606 --> 33:45.981
Come on.

34:00.789 --> 34:03.582
Come on.

34:03.709 --> 34:07.128
In and out just like
a couple of ghosts.

34:07.254 --> 34:08.545
Gimme that.

34:12.217 --> 34:13.801
Thank you, sir.

34:23.311 --> 34:25.896
You got a safe?

34:41.830 --> 34:44.123
Christ!

34:44.248 --> 34:46.000
Go, go, go, go!

34:53.049 --> 34:55.551
Fuck you!

34:57.763 --> 34:59.054
God damn it!

34:59.639 --> 34:59.680
God damn it,
I can't believe that.

34:59.681 --> 35:03.934
God damn it,
I can't believe that.

35:04.060 --> 35:06.937
Shit.

35:07.063 --> 35:08.606
I'll tell you what, boy.

35:08.732 --> 35:10.649
Life can be
such a bore sometimes.

35:10.776 --> 35:15.362
But this...
This is great.

35:15.489 --> 35:19.074
Well, don't
look at me like that.

35:19.075 --> 35:22.661
You and me make
a really, really good team.

35:22.788 --> 35:26.165
Shit, they probably got
nicknames for us already.

35:26.291 --> 35:28.000
Who? The papers?

35:28.084 --> 35:30.878
Yeah.

35:31.004 --> 35:32.404
Don't they have
better things to do?

35:32.464 --> 35:35.090
Shit, no. Bonnie and Clyde
was all over the newspapers.

35:35.091 --> 35:37.426
Billy the Kid, too.
He was famous.

35:37.552 --> 35:39.094
Like in movies?

35:39.179 --> 35:42.097
- Exactly.
- Mm-hmm.

35:42.182 --> 35:47.144
You know, in the movies,
they all got shot to death.

35:50.106 --> 35:52.107
Aren't you having fun?

35:52.108 --> 35:53.818
If I was your age,
I'd be having fun.

35:53.944 --> 35:56.654
No, I'm not having fun.

36:00.116 --> 36:01.826
You think this
is easy for me?

36:01.952 --> 36:04.119
Dragging your skinny
little ass all over the place?

36:04.120 --> 36:06.121
This ain't no fucking
holiday, all right?

36:06.122 --> 36:07.998
This is a job.

36:08.124 --> 36:10.084
This is work driving you home.

36:14.214 --> 36:17.424
You know, it'll all be
over soon enough, all right?

36:17.551 --> 36:19.385
Yeah, I hope so.

36:22.430 --> 36:26.141
Did you, uh...

36:26.142 --> 36:29.603
Did you see that shotgun under
the counter earlier today?

36:29.729 --> 36:30.855
No.

36:30.981 --> 36:32.147
No?

36:32.232 --> 36:33.858
I just figured you
might have seen it

36:33.984 --> 36:35.943
underneath there when you
were, you know, down below...

36:36.069 --> 36:38.153
I didn't see any gun.

36:39.447 --> 36:41.365
Okay.

36:47.080 --> 36:48.747
