in the freezer.

36:53.962 --> 36:57.172
Okay. Well, we'd like
one scoop.

36:57.173 --> 36:58.966
Two spoons for me
and the boy, please.

36:59.092 --> 37:01.886
One scoop and two spoons.

37:02.012 --> 37:02.887
Two spoons.
That's right.

37:03.013 --> 37:04.430
Okay.

37:09.185 --> 37:10.227
Let's go.

37:10.353 --> 37:12.313
Whoa, whoa, whoa.
Ice cream.

37:12.439 --> 37:14.315
We're leaving.
Come on.

37:14.441 --> 37:17.109
- We have plenty of money.
- We gotta keep moving.

37:17.193 --> 37:18.313
I'm not even done
eating yet.

37:18.403 --> 37:20.946
Yes, you are.
Let's go.

37:31.458 --> 37:33.208
Get out here!

37:35.211 --> 37:36.462
God damn it.

37:36.588 --> 37:41.342
Here we go, honey.
One scoop and two spoons.

37:41.468 --> 37:42.468
I love chocolate.

37:42.510 --> 37:43.552
Thank you.

37:43.678 --> 37:46.221
Oh, he just needed
some fresh air.

37:46.306 --> 37:48.515
Uh, he'll be back, right?

37:48.642 --> 37:49.767
- Yes.
- Okay.

37:49.893 --> 37:54.229
I can share if you want some.

37:54.230 --> 37:55.356
Honey, I don't
need the calories.

37:55.482 --> 37:57.733
You enjoy that
chocolate ice cream.

37:57.859 --> 37:59.985
Let me know if I can
do something for you.

38:00.111 --> 38:01.654
Thank you.

38:15.418 --> 38:17.920
That'll be $14.50.

38:18.046 --> 38:19.046
Thank you.

38:19.172 --> 38:20.839
You're welcome, sweetie.

38:24.135 --> 38:25.511
I'll tell you what.

38:25.637 --> 38:29.390
You tell his mama that
she raised a gem of a boy.

38:29.516 --> 38:31.809
Yeah, I'll be sure
to tell her that.

39:25.030 --> 39:27.489
We gotta get rid
of that truck.

39:27.615 --> 39:29.033
I like that truck.

39:29.159 --> 39:32.453
Yeah, well, it's not
safe to drive anymore.

40:05.070 --> 40:07.237
Come on, let's go.

40:13.870 --> 40:15.621
Hey, hey, hey! Hey!

40:15.747 --> 40:20.501
Come on, lady!
I got a kid here!

40:20.627 --> 40:21.627
Jesus Christ.

40:21.669 --> 40:22.961
We should have
kept the truck.

40:23.088 --> 40:25.672
Yeah, well...

40:25.799 --> 40:29.093
Hey!

40:29.219 --> 40:32.596
Just keep walking.
Just keep walking.

40:37.310 --> 40:38.185
Shit!

40:38.311 --> 40:39.770
Keep your mouth shut.

40:39.896 --> 40:42.272
Neither one of us want
to go to jail, right?

40:49.197 --> 40:50.864
Hello, Officer!

40:52.200 --> 40:54.201
Hitchhiking is illegal.

40:54.327 --> 40:56.411
Particularly on Sunday.

40:56.412 --> 40:58.789
Yeah, our car broke down.

40:58.915 --> 41:02.417
Uh-huh.
Let me see some ID.

41:02.418 --> 41:04.169
Come on.

41:07.507 --> 41:10.968
Turn around, over there.
Spread your legs. Come on.

41:11.094 --> 41:12.302
Where you headed?

41:12.428 --> 41:16.431
Uh, his grandparents' place.

41:16.432 --> 41:18.308
I'm real sorry
about this, officer.

41:18.434 --> 41:21.186
It's just that, you know,
we didn't have much of a choice.

41:21.312 --> 41:24.481
Our truck broke
down back there, so...

41:24.607 --> 41:27.442
Well, now is it a car
or is it a truck?

41:30.029 --> 41:31.822
He meant car.

41:31.948 --> 41:33.991
You better both come with me.

41:34.117 --> 41:35.784
We'll clear this up
down at the station.

41:35.910 --> 41:37.578
Come on.

41:45.170 --> 41:47.212
Uh, sir?

41:47.338 --> 41:49.715
We're just on our
way to church.

41:49.841 --> 41:51.383
What was that?

41:51.467 --> 41:54.636
We're going to church
to pray for my mom.

41:54.762 --> 41:57.055
Yeah, his mama died.

41:57.182 --> 41:58.765
- Is that right?
- Yeah.

41:58.892 --> 42:01.476
Is that right, son?
Your mama just died?

42:01.561 --> 42:04.479
Yes, sir.
Just last week.

42:04.480 --> 42:07.232
I'm sorry to hear that.

42:07.358 --> 42:08.817
All right, get in the car.
I'll give you a ride.

42:08.943 --> 42:10.360
- Come on.
- No, no, we can do...

42:10.486 --> 42:12.154
No, it's all right.
Don't worry.

42:12.280 --> 42:15.073
Come on.
Don't make me wait.

42:15.200 --> 42:17.284
Can I sit in the front?

42:17.410 --> 42:19.870
Sure.

42:24.375 --> 42:24.458
Thank you, Officer!

42:24.459 --> 42:26.501
Thank you, Officer!

42:29.714 --> 42:33.467
All right, let's get
the hell out of here.

42:33.551 --> 42:37.221
Hey, where you going?

42:37.347 --> 42:38.639
Church.

42:38.765 --> 42:40.515
Louis?

