01:10:23.761 --> 01:10:26.138
A brazen daytime robbery
of the Alpine Savings Bank

01:10:26.222 --> 01:10:28.432
has state police looking
for an unidentified man

01:10:28.558 --> 01:10:30.475
and his teenage accomplice.

01:10:30.602 --> 01:10:34.187
They were last seen traveling
west on Farm Road 369

01:10:34.188 --> 01:10:39.192
in a tan station wagon with
Texas license plates 74EJQ8.

01:10:44.699 --> 01:10:45.908
Are we going to jail?

01:10:46.034 --> 01:10:47.993
Nah, we ain't
going to jail.

01:10:50.788 --> 01:10:52.539
You scared?

01:10:52.665 --> 01:10:54.207
No.

01:10:56.377 --> 01:10:58.170
I'm scared.

01:10:59.213 --> 01:11:03.550
What are we gonna do?

01:11:03.676 --> 01:11:05.385
I don't know.

01:11:08.222 --> 01:11:11.099
Oh, what a mess.

01:11:14.687 --> 01:11:16.563
We should go to Mexico.

01:11:18.316 --> 01:11:21.401
We could live there for
years with all this money.

01:11:21.527 --> 01:11:25.155
We should get a car, but...

01:11:25.239 --> 01:11:26.949
we could do that.

01:11:27.075 --> 01:11:30.369
- Give me a rock.
- Oh, I got it.

01:12:11.369 --> 01:12:13.954
I liked the
station wagon better.

01:12:14.080 --> 01:12:18.291
Yeah, well, nobody's gonna
be missing this piece of shit.

01:12:18.292 --> 01:12:20.293
I can tell you that much.

01:12:20.378 --> 01:12:24.214
Be nice if we could
this thing up over 50.

01:12:24.298 --> 01:12:26.258
I figure we'll drive
about halfway there

01:12:26.342 --> 01:12:28.510
then find a quiet place
to camp for the night.

01:12:30.596 --> 01:12:32.305
What's it gonna be like?

01:12:32.306 --> 01:12:35.434
What?
Your grandparents' place?

01:12:35.560 --> 01:12:37.978
Yep.

01:12:39.022 --> 01:12:40.647
I don't know.

01:12:40.773 --> 01:12:42.983
I imagine it'll be beautiful.

01:12:47.905 --> 01:12:50.407
Think we'll be there tomorrow?

01:12:50.533 --> 01:12:54.119
Oh, yeah.
We should be there by lunch.

01:12:56.372 --> 01:12:59.332
First we have to make it
through the desert.

01:13:01.419 --> 01:13:03.962
Then we'll cross
into the mountains.

01:13:07.050 --> 01:13:11.261
We'll know we're getting close
when we can see the farmlands.

01:13:11.345 --> 01:13:15.140
Green, as far as
the eye can see.

01:13:20.271 --> 01:13:23.315
Just like
that picture?

01:13:25.026 --> 01:13:28.361
Yeah, just like
the picture.

01:14:36.806 --> 01:14:40.433
Let me get that for you.

01:14:46.107 --> 01:14:47.482
There you go.

01:14:52.446 --> 01:14:55.115
You're looking
good there, partner.

01:14:55.241 --> 01:14:56.616
I want to make
a good impression, you know?

01:14:56.742 --> 01:14:58.451
Let's go.

01:15:23.477 --> 01:15:25.020
Fill it up, will you?

01:15:37.783 --> 01:15:40.869
- Morning.
- Good morning.

01:16:04.602 --> 01:16:07.520
He almost
finished out there?

01:16:07.605 --> 01:16:08.855
Yeah, almost.

01:16:17.531 --> 01:16:19.950
9-1-1.
What's your emergency?

01:16:20.993 --> 01:16:24.454
Hello?

01:16:24.538 --> 01:16:26.706
What's the address
of your emergency?

01:16:30.544 --> 01:16:31.586
That'll be it.

01:16:31.712 --> 01:16:34.547
Okay, it's $20 on pump, $24.

01:16:34.548 --> 01:16:36.800
$24. That's a steal.

01:16:42.556 --> 01:16:44.557
You have a good day.

01:16:51.816 --> 01:16:53.566
Boy?

01:17:00.950 --> 01:17:02.742
You're the one
from the paper.

01:17:02.868 --> 01:17:07.372
I think you got me confused
with somebody else, all right?

01:17:07.498 --> 01:17:09.582
No. I know who you are.

01:17:09.583 --> 01:17:11.960
I know who he is too.

01:17:27.768 --> 01:17:31.146
The truth, sir...

01:17:37.528 --> 01:17:40.613
The truth is,
he's my son

01:17:40.614 --> 01:17:43.616
and all I've ever done
is disappoint him.

01:17:46.787 --> 01:17:49.289
I've abandoned him.

01:17:49.415 --> 01:17:52.417
I've lied to him.

01:17:52.543 --> 01:17:55.211
I found every
excuse that I can

01:17:55.338 --> 01:17:58.631
just to make him another
mistake in my life.

01:17:58.716 --> 01:18:02.635
A secret that
I keep to myself.

01:18:06.140 --> 01:18:08.641
But he won't let me.

01:18:08.642 --> 01:18:12.812
Please, just
let me make it right.

01:18:14.565 --> 01:18:17.275
Just please
let me make it right.

01:18:25.659 --> 01:18:27.911
Come on.
Grab your bag!

01:18:28.037 --> 01:18:30.663
Don't you hear that?

01:18:30.748 --> 01:18:34.209
Do you remember
the address?

01:18:34.335 --> 01:18:35.585
What?

01:18:35.669 --> 01:18:37.337
Do you remember
what the place looks like?

01:18:37.463 --> 01:18:39.672
Do you remember the address?

01:18:39.673 --> 01:18:43.218
What's going on?

01:18:43.344 --> 01:18:45.929
All right, I need
you to leave.

01:18:46.055 --> 01:18:47.430
I'm not leaving you.

01:18:47.556 --> 01:18:49.682
I promised this guy
in there I wouldn't run

01:18:49.683 --> 01:18:51.851
'cause I can't run anymore.

01:18:55.314 --> 01:18:58.691
I see myself as a person
that I'm supposed to be.

01:18:58.692 --> 01:19:02.237
A good person, the kind
of person that you deserve.

01:19:02.363 --> 01:19:04.239
I just...

01:19:04.365 --> 01:19:05.573
I don't have the courage
to be that person.

01:19:05.699 --> 01:19:06.783
I don't have the courage
to change.

01:19:06.909 --> 01:19:08.701
Do you understand
what I'm trying to say?

01:19:08.786 --> 01:19:10.995
Here, take this with you.

01:19:11.122 --> 01:19:14.499
Take it with you, and go.

01:19:14.625 --> 01:19:16.585
I need you to go, all right?
You're gonna be okay.

01:19:16.710 --> 01:19:18.795
Hey, you're gonna
be all right.

01:19:18.921 --> 01:19:20.713
Now go, go, go, go.

01:19:20.798 --> 01:19:23.299
I don't want to leave, John.
I don't want to leave you.

01:19:23.426 --> 01:19:26.386
You gotta go. Go.

01:19:26.512 --> 01:19:27.387
I don't want to leave you, John.

01:19:27.513 --> 01:19:29.180
Go! Run, god damn it!

01:19:29.306 --> 01:19:30.849
Run!

01:19:46.031 --> 01:19:48.616
Face the car!
Hands in the air!

01:21:47.361 --> 01:21:52.115
What do you think it's going to be like?

01:21:52.241 --> 01:21:54.450
I'd imagine it'd be beautiful.

01:21:56.579 --> 01:21:59.330
Surrounded by farmland as
far as the eye can see.

01:22:01.959 --> 01:22:04.877
Just like that picture?

01:22:04.878 --> 01:22:09.132
Yeah, just like
the picture.

01:22:38.078 --> 01:22:40.455
We're going to do
a quick line inspection here

01:22:40.581 --> 01:22:42.624
in Farmington, New Mexico.

01:22:42.750 --> 01:22:44.167
Line number seven.

01:24:57.092 --> 01:24:59.385
You lost?

01:25:06.769 --> 01:25:09.020
I need to get
to Farmington.

01:25:09.104 --> 01:25:12.732
You are lost.

01:25:12.858 --> 01:25:14.150
I'm not lost.

01:25:14.276 --> 01:25:17.069
Oh, whatever you say.

01:25:17.154 --> 01:25:20.865
Yeah, you're close.

01:25:23.076 --> 01:25:26.704
It's up that road about
an hour or so.

01:25:28.457 --> 01:25:30.082
An hour?

01:25:30.083 --> 01:25:33.836
Yeah,
at least an hour.

01:25:33.962 --> 01:25:36.214
But you're young.

01:25:43.096 --> 01:25:46.182
You could give me a ride.

01:25:46.308 --> 01:25:49.101
I could, yeah.

01:25:51.146 --> 01:25:56.025
I'd be a lot more willing if
we was to bargain for it.

01:25:56.109 --> 01:25:58.361
Kid with that kind of
silver ain't gonna have

01:25:58.487 --> 01:26:01.739
a hard time finding
a ride home.

01:26:05.118 --> 01:26:07.370
How about it, kid?

01:26:18.799 --> 01:26:23.469
23 Farm Road. 23 Farm Road.

01:27:46.428 --> 01:27:49.221
Louis?

01:27:49.222 --> 01:27:50.723
Hey, Grandma.

01:27:50.849 --> 01:27:53.225
Oh, thank you, Lord!

01:27:53.310 --> 01:27:56.896
Oh, we thought
we'd lost you forever!

01:27:59.232 --> 01:28:03.194
You were supposed
to be here days ago.

01:28:03.278 --> 01:28:05.237
Just look at you.

01:28:05.238 --> 01:28:07.573
How'd you get here?

01:28:07.699 --> 01:28:09.241
I walked.

01:28:09.242 --> 01:28:10.785
Oh, Lord.

01:28:10.911 --> 01:28:13.621
Well, come on in the house.

01:28:13.747 --> 01:28:15.790
Where'd you start from?

01:28:15.916 --> 01:28:17.917
What do you mean,
you walked?

01:28:29.471 --> 01:28:32.264
How do you boys
get so dirty?

01:28:34.267 --> 01:28:37.269
It's good to have
you home, sweetheart.

01:28:37.270 --> 01:28:41.273
I want this to feel
like home, okay?

01:28:53.787 --> 01:28:56.414
This was your mother's room.

01:29:01.503 --> 01:29:04.171
I kept so many of 'em.

01:29:05.465 --> 01:29:09.093
I hope they
don't make you sad.

01:29:09.219 --> 01:29:11.303
I like looking at 'em.

01:29:13.932 --> 01:29:16.684
Makes me feel like
she's still here.

01:29:18.895 --> 01:29:22.648
You were born in this bed.
This exact one.

01:29:23.984 --> 01:29:25.484
Really?

01:29:29.823 --> 01:29:31.574
See?

01:29:31.700 --> 01:29:34.869
There's your mom and
your dad holding you.

01:29:36.538 --> 01:29:38.914
You were just
a few months old.

01:29:40.751 --> 01:29:44.462
Oh, you've grown
so much since then.

01:29:47.549 --> 01:29:49.341
Oh, my sweet boy.

